Rating: 3
I make this wonderful cake every Christmas. It keeps well over the holidays and is sturdy enough to mail, provided it's sealed up in a tin. One year I even sent one to New Zealand. One caveat: don't forget to add the flour. It's easy to forget, since it's not mentioned in the recipe text.

